metadata.description: The WatchCharts Junghans Market Index is an indicator of the secondary market performance of Junghans watches. It is composed of the top 20 models within the brand, sorted and weighted by transaction value. The index shows the average market price (in USD) of these 20 watches over time, and is rebalanced once per year on January 1.
